Bosse_Exdeath_Status_Deep Freeze_Desc: Your body is encased in ice, preventing action and dealing damage over time.
Bosse_Exdeath_Status_Doom_Desc: Certain death when counter reaches zero.
Bosse_Exdeath_Status_Paralysis_Desc: Deadened nerves are sometimes preventing the execution of actions.
Bosse_Exdeath_Status_Pyretic_Desc: Fire-aspected damage is taken with every action.
Bosse_Exdeath_Status_Zombification_Desc: Turned into a mindless zombie under enemy control.
ContentDesc_Deltametrie 4.0: And so you come to the final encounter in the Deltascape. Awaiting you is yet another villain from a work of fiction known as Exdeath, who is described as an evil tree that assumes the form of a dark mage. Doubt not but that this will be your toughest test yet, but overcome it you must if you are to head off Omega's threat.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17800_Text: Hahaha... You shall all be given to the void!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17802_Text: My magic is steeped in the greatest of powersâ”€the power of the void!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17803_Text: My true strength lies in the void, and in the void all is laid bare!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17804_Text: You will rue provoking me! I shall send you to your doom!
